{"tid":1584950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"可以答應我嗎? 用一輩子來抵制黨鐵。","createTime":"2019-09-21T11:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T12:30:54.000Z","uid":293022,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"99b70c4c33565dbc4aa1d404b495c98cc25745ae","tid":1584950,"uid":293022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:22:39.000Z","msg":"1) 罷塔黨鐵<br />\n2) 罷買所有黨鐵商店<br />\n3) <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kexX5v7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkexX5v7.jpg&h=e7d70b7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張八達通已經用到 -8.xx，而我已經立志永遠都吾會再用八達通，比黨鐵賺果2%。<br />\n<br />\n已經無用八達通一個星期，每次出街，返工，放工都好吾方便。但一直以黎，我地都貪圖左呢種方便好耐，黨鐵先有機會好似今時今日甘樣壟斷法。<br />\n<br />\n吾可以再甘落去! 一定要繼續抗爭!! <br />\n<br />\n吾知有幾大作用，但做到既，我都會去做!"},{"pid":"fcd138d8382b11cdbbb55c64767709f5cbf72f2c","tid":1584950,"uid":123713,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:23:00.000Z","msg":"[行動又無人理？] 全球最大親子抗爭活動上線啦！ <strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">#birdfoldingchallenge</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1584614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1584614</a><br />\n摺一隻紙鳥，影相，放上Facebook / Twitter / Instagram，並加上hashtag #birdfoldingchallenge #929globalmarch #929GlobalAntiTotalitarianism，copy呢段文字再tag 5個朋友，就完成！</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYhkXcO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiYhkXcO.jpg&h=9b11593e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ef9b1715ad19dec4e5eb9a9123e46bab87f6daf","tid":1584950,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"3a98037bbf56b94d23c1e833c302185752c91273","tid":1584950,"uid":81812,"like"